title: flex queue is fucked tbh
body:
ended season 6 in gold 5 with a 47% win rate cause i only wanted to get to gold.
I go 6-5 in my placements and I end up getting plat 4. I mean what the fuck.

btw, the reason why I played 11 placements is because there was a remake because the beta client didn't let me swap champs with someone else.
